summary: Aggretsuko’s season 2 felt like it was personally attacking me, but it’s still as entertaining as the first season. A gift. ...
body:
Aggretsuko’s season 2 felt like it was personally attacking me, but it’s still as entertaining as the first season. A gift. 

Kinda needed more Fenneko imo. And i still want to put Haida in my pocket to protect him from the world and give him every happiness. What an incredible, hopeless dork.
